<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Catamaran:200,400,700,800,900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/pixi.js/5.1.3/pixi.min.js"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/queueStyle.css">
    <script src= "/socket.io/socket.io.js"></script>
    <script type='text/javascript'>const POST =  <%- data %>;</script>
  </head>
  <body>
    <canvas id="font"></canvas>
    <div style='visibility: hidden;' id='changelog' onmouseover="toggle_changelog()" onmouseout="toggle_changelog()">
      <h1>OBSTAR changelog pre-lauch 1.0.0 *Click on me*: </h1>

      &nbsp&nbsp  - Welcome to the first version of Obstar ! A 'fangame' of "insert THE game here" made by me, 17 (18 now) years old kid who love video game.<br> *Also, I'm french so sorry for the spelling :/*<br><br>
      &emsp;- 3 game modes: Free For all / 2 team / 4 team;<br><br>
      &emsp;- Colored name base on your xp;<br><br>
      &emsp;- A level system (wich do nothing... for now)<br><br>
      <h1>Coming soon (or less soon) :</h1>
      &emsp;- More game modes;<br><br>
      &emsp;- A lot more tanks;<br><br>
      &emsp;- A system of weekly or monthly tanks rotation;<br><br>
      &emsp;- More stuff to do with the xp;<br><br>
      &emsp;- A twitter !<br><br>
      &emsp;- A leaderboard;<br><br>
      &emsp;- leagues / clans / friends;<br><br>
      &emsp;- Extra special color names;<br><br>
            &emsp;- Boss !<br><br>
    </div>
    <div class="center_box">
      <div class="gm_zone white_box">
        <span>Select the game mode !</span>
        <div id='ffa_button' class='gm_button' onmousedown="selectGameMode('ffa')">Free for All</div>
        <div id='team2_button' class='gm_button' onmousedown="selectGameMode('2team')">2 Teams vs</div>
        <div id='team4_button' class='gm_button' onmousedown="selectGameMode('4team')">4 Teams vs</div>
        <span class='coming-soon'>Coming soon...<span>
      </div>
      <div class='profil_zone white_box'>
        <div class='obstar noselec'>OBstar</div>
        <div id='pseudo' class='pseudo noselec'>unamed</div>
        <div class='lvl noselec'><span id='lvl'>1</span><div class='bar-back'><div id='bar-front' class='bar-front'></div><div id='bar-info'>0 / 1000</div></div></div>
        <div id='xp' class='xp noselec'>0 xp</div>
        <input id='player_name' type='text' class='input-name' value='unamed' maxlength="16" placeholder="Tank Name">
        <button id='play_button' class='input-play noselec' onclick='queue()'>> Play</button>
        <div class='graphic noselec'>
          <span>Graphic</span>
          <input id='resolution' type='range' class='input-ranger' min='0.5' max='1.6' step='0.1' value='1.2'>
          <span id='quality'>Good<span>
        </div>
        <div class='upgrade_panel'>
          <div class='upLogo noselec'>Colored Name !</div>
          <div id="colorname" class='name-color upgrade_box noselec'>
            <div id='rightcolorama' class='arrow' onclick='colorama_go_left()'><</div>
            <div id='colorama' class='colorama'>
            </div>
            <div id='leftcolorama' class='arrow' onclick='colorama_go_right()'>></div>
          </div>
          <div class='coming-soon noselec'>More And More Coming Soon..!</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class='info_zone white_box'>
      </div>
    </div>
    <form class = 'disconnect' method="post" action='connect'>
      <input type='hidden' name='disconnect' value='1'>
      <input type='submit' value='disconnect'>
    </form>
    <script src="/font.js"></script>
    <script src="/queue.js"></script>
  </body>
</html
